Home
About us

PPG Industries, Inc.


PPG Industries company is a leader in its markets; as a streamlined, efficient manufacturer; PPG company operates at the leading edge of new technologies and solutions. It is our vision to continue being the world's leading coatings and specialty products and services company, serving customers in construction, consumer products, industrial and transportation markets and aftermarkets. PPG has manufacturing facilities and equity affiliates in more than 60 countries around the globe.
At PPG, Innovation is Nothing New  As the world leader in coatings and specialty materials today, we have always led with innovation. We truly believe that innovation is a rite of survival, not only for our company, but for our customers as well.
Ahead of the Green Wave  Sustainability has long been an underlying principle at PPG company. Many of the innovations we've introduced over recent years have provided our customers with an environmental or sustainability advantage. In the paint industry, we were one of the earliest pioneers to introduce low-volatile organic compound (VOC) products.
Leading In Colour  Besides our focus on innovation and sustainability, there is another chapter in PPG's success story: our colour leadership. Our presence in a wide array of business and geographic markets gives us a unique vantage point from which to observe and translate emerging global colour trends for our customers' applications - from consumer goods to automotive colour, from residential to commercial, to consumer goods and industrial design.
Quality  The key to further strengthening PPG operations is our Total Quality Process. Through teamwork and individual actions, every PPG associate is challenged to continuously devise ways of improving their job, as well as related processes. The focus is on the customer; learning their exact needs; doing the right things the first time, every time; and giving customers the product they want, when they want it. In short, continuously striving for total customer satisfaction.
 
Bringing Innovation to the Surface™ is a trademark of PPG Industries Ohio, Inc.

